{
  "chapter": 266,
  "chapter_summary": "第266章《漳水之战》讲述寇仲与商秀洵率牧场精骑千人夜袭曹应龙贼军粮车，以火攻瘫痪敌军后勤。随后寇仲与商震大军会师，分兵两路追击至漳水东岸。曹应龙背水布阵，暗中搭浮桥欲偷渡。徐子陵率宣永在对岸设伏，以投石机击断浮桥制造混乱，虚张声势疑兵之计令敌军崩溃。寇仲趁势全面进攻，徐子陵持榴木棍身先士卒，少帅军与牧场战士头扎黄带以示敌我，展开惨烈歼灭战。曹军全军覆没，曹应龙与房见鼎仅率百余人仓皇逃窜，徐子陵紧追不舍。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "现在尽管我们只得一千人，要胜他们仍非没有把握。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 11,
      "line_end": 13
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "今次我们非是要求只打一场胜仗，而是要把这些为害人世的贼寇彻底消灭，又要把自己的伤亡减至最低。那才显出本事。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 17
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "text": "陶叔盛怎曾被这些流寇收买，致背叛牧场呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 19,
      "line_end": 21
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "曹应龙怎买得动他，收买他的是李密！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 25
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_wen_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "白文原",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "队首的骑兵与队尾的运粮车相隔达三里之遥，只要我们手脚够快，可在敌骑掉头来援救前，及时全师退走。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 29,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "寇仲成功了，否则曹应龙不会在白天赶路。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 85,
      "line_end": 87
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "据探子说，敌人队形散乱，完全是狼奔鼠窜、落荒而逃的格局，曹应龙今趟该是穷途末路了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 89,
      "line_end": 91
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "今晚我必以此棍取曹应龙的狗命。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 95,
      "line_end": 97
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "曹应龙果然有两下子，不过却犯下两个大错。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 111,
      "line_end": 111
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_fang",
      "speaker_name": "骆方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我却觉得他现在用的战略非常高明，我们若贸然进攻，必伤亡惨重。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 113,
      "line_end": 115
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "他只是虚有其表，首先他粮草全失，饿着肚子能战得多久，我们只要把他困死在这里，他只能以全军覆没收场，这是第一个错误。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 117,
      "line_end": 119
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "第二个错误，是他以为我不知道他在等待天黑好铺搭浮桥，然后偷偷渡江。此计本来妙绝，却不知对岸另有伏兵，正在恭候他的贼驾。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 121,
      "line_end": 125
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_luo_fang",
      "speaker_name": "骆方",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "我们该于何时进攻？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 131,
      "line_end": 131
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_luo_fang",
      "text": "这要由徐子陵来决定，当他们在对岸放出烟花讯号时，就是曹贼以鲜血来偿还所有欠债的一刻。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 133,
      "line_end": 135
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点燃火把，竖立在每个丘顶处，同时挖掘战壕，我要教敌人没有一个能漏网。牧场兵必胜，贼兵必败！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 141
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "假若曹应龙依样葫芦，命渡江者亦在这边结阵，以我们的兵力，恐怕奈何不了他。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 149,
      "line_end": 151
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "若在一般正常的情势下，我们确奈何不了他。但你仔细看清楚他们，人人均露出饥疲交迫的神色，只要你那八台投石机能制造点混乱，例如击断其中一道浮桥，保证敌入不战自溃，无论结成甚么阵势都不会起作用。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 155,
      "line_end": 158
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "我确是有点患得患失。我们是故意养精蓄锐，又是攻其不备，我知彼而彼不知我，实立于不败之地。嘿！徐爷怎能在这种大战一触即发的关头，仍然如此气定神闲的？",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 161,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "只要你能把生死成败得失，完全不放在心上，自能神闲意适，亦只有如此才可把能力完全发挥出来。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xuan_yong",
      "speaker_name": "宣永",
      "listener": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "text": "宣永受教！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 171,
      "line_end": 171
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": "char_xuan_yong",
      "text": "曹应龙和房见鼎已渡江啦！向霸先就便宜寇仲吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 179,
      "line_end": 181
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xu_zi_ling",
      "speaker_name": "徐子陵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "点火把！",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 183,
      "line_end": 183
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_xiu_xun",
      "speaker_name": "商秀洵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为何有这么多人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 191,
      "line_end": 191
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好小子！竟懂得虚张声势，连我都给他吓倒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 193,
      "line_end": 193
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "进攻！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 266,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 204
    }
  ],
